<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Key Implementations in Alonzo and Their Impact</h3>



<p>The Alonzo <a href="https://securenest.org/learn/cardano-network-upgrades">upgrade to the Cardano blockchain</a> introduced smart contract functionality, marking a significant pivot towards a more versatile and programmable infrastructure. You&#8217;ve witnessed Cardano evolve into a third-generation blockchain platform, capable of hosting complex dapps on Cardano with Alonzo&#8217;s deployment.</p>



